{"tid":978594,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【學習】usdcad最近走勢分解","createTime":"2019-01-12T04:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T07:41:43.000Z","uid":76531,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"913e26ddf79dea725b04e2d35ec863fc3fef7a56","tid":978594,"uid":76531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T04:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oNns9GA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoNns9GA.png&h=d88094a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n綠色段可以看做短期走勢，白色中期走勢，藍色長期走勢。<br />\n結論：<br />\n預期會出現藍色的向上段。<br />\n理由：<br />\n1.藍色段來到前面藍色段的低點，有一定支撐作用。<br />\n2.最後段藍色段內出現背馳。（macd黃白線與柱體面積都減弱）<br />\n3.參考最近藍色段末端的次級別（白色段）都是W底或M頂。現在再次出現W底且突破頸線。"},{"pid":"d998d382d30e1ff013310b164d959ee35bddd9cb","tid":978594,"uid":31525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T05:51:36.000Z","msg":"終於有FX post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5abc7f637438032217b4dcb30e58490a2b13ca88","tid":978594,"uid":76531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T04:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hNxZwis.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhNxZwis.png&h=ae11fd05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4h死叉，段內背馳，38.2壓力，藍色向下？<br />\n5破3,6低4介入，4止蝕."},{"pid":"ba358a7dcfc4dac9f18d85ac32e6a721c82ed62b","tid":978594,"uid":80392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:41:43.000Z","msg":"Lm高汁"}]}